snippet.title: Slime Rancher: Deluxe Edition - Retail Pre-Order Announcement!
snippet.description:
Slime Rancher: Deluxe Edition is coming to PS4 and Xbox One in early April! You can pick it up at retail or preorder at shop.skybound.com! The Deluxe Edition includes all previous DLC with additional content:
* The Secret Style Pack
* Slimepedia booklet
* Original Soundtrack 1 + 2, and more!

Take home this wildly popular sandbox game to play anytime and never worry about losing your game in the cloud. Pick it up at retail stores or preorder the game at shop.skybound.com.
